== 制作 ==

=== 初期發展 ===

當《[[星球大戰|星球大戰]]》正傳三部曲正式完結後，該系列導演兼創作者[[喬治·盧卡斯|喬治·盧卡斯]]多次討論過續集三部曲的敘事走向，但完全否決將其拍攝的打算<ref name="LATimes2008">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/la-et-lucas7-2008may07,0,7983947.story|title=George Lucas: 'Star Wars' won't go beyond Darth Vader|last=Boucher|first=Geoff|date=2008-05-07|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|accessdate=2012-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023143206/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/la-et-lucas7-2008may07,0,7983947.story|archive-date=2012-10-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年12月，他將自己的公司[[盧卡斯影業|盧卡斯影業]]以及《星球大戰》和《奪寶奇兵》的所有權賣給了[[華特迪士尼公司|華特迪士尼公司]]<ref name="BloombergMar2013" />。在與[[盧卡斯影業|盧卡斯影業]]新總裁[[凱斯琳·甘迺迪_(電影監製)|凱斯琳·甘迺迪]]（好萊塢最有權勢的電影監製，同時也是盧卡斯的好友）一同出席採訪時，盧卡斯說到：“我總是說我不會再做任何與《星際大戰》有關的電影了，而這是事實 - 因為我不會再做下去了。但這並不意味着我不願意讓凱斯琳將該系列發揚光大。”{{NoteTag|1=原文："I always said I wasn't going to do any more and that's true, because I'm not going to do any more, but that doesn't mean I'm unwilling to turn it over to Kathy to do more."}}<ref>{{cite web|last1=Nakashima|first1=Ryan|title=Disney to make new 'Star Wars' films, buy Lucas co|url=http://finance.yahoo.com/news/disney-star-wars-films-buy-210830937.html|publisher={{link-en|Yahoo! Finance|Yahoo! Finance}}|accessdate=2015-12-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030233227/http://finance.yahoo.com/news/disney-star-wars-films-buy-210830937.html|archivedate=2012-10-30|deadurl=no|location=Los Angeles, California|date=2012-10-30}}</ref>

作為原力覺醒的創意顧問（{{lang-en|Creative Consultant}}），盧卡斯出席了多項與該片故事情節有關的會議，並對[[星球大戰|星球大戰]]電影宇宙中的多項細節做出建議<ref name="BloombergMar2013"/>。盧卡斯在迪士尼收購《星球大戰》版權時也將自己寫的續集三部曲故事大綱給予新製作組用於借鑒和審閲，但是新製作組決定另起爐灶，並告訴盧卡斯他“對這部片子的參與將到此為止”。盧卡斯的兒子傑特告訴英國《[[衛報|衛報]]》說：“雖然我父親親手拍板讓[[J·J·亞伯拉罕|J·J·亞伯拉罕]]執導這部片子，他仍然對將該系列出售給迪士尼一事感到心痛。而父親雖然在很多方面想引領新劇組，但他還是想放手，讓這部系列由新一代電影工作者來引領。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/oct/09/star-wars-george-lucas-jj-abrams|title=Star Wars sequels: George Lucas 'constantly talking' to JJ Abrams|last=Child|first=Ben|date=2013-10-09|accessdate=2015-01-23|work=The Guardian|location=UK|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010083951/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/oct/09/star-wars-george-lucas-jj-abrams|archive-date=2014-10-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年11月，盧卡斯說迪士尼對他的參與並不熱衷，並承認：“如果我在新劇組的話，我只會製造麻煩，因為他們不會採納我的想法和建議，而我早就對這部電影（以及整個系列）的未來失去了控制。即使我強制讓他們聽從於我，一切只會往更糟的方向發展。”

原力覺醒的第一版草稿是由[[邁克爾·阿恩特|邁克爾·阿恩特]]編寫<ref>{{cite web|last=Brodesser-Akner|first=Claude|title=Update: Toy Story 3's Michael Arndt Confirmed As Star Wars: Episode VII Writer|url=http://www.vulture.com/2012/11/star-wars-episode-vii-may-have-found-its-writer.html|accessdate=2014-05-23|work=Vulture|date=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140524024731/http://www.vulture.com/2012/11/star-wars-episode-vii-may-have-found-its-writer.html|archive-date=2014-05-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Kit|first=Borys|title=New 'Star Wars' Movie Has Treatment by 'Toy Story 3' Writer|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/new-star-wars-movie-has-387784|accessdate=2014-05-23|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828133757/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/new-star-wars-movie-has-387784|archive-date=2014-08-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Kit|first=Borys|title=Lucasfilm Confirms Michael Arndt to Write 'Star Wars: Episode VII'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/new-star-wars-movie-michael-388424|accessdate=2013-10-24|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2012-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022121103/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/new-star-wars-movie-michael-388424|archive-date=2013-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Hiatt">{{cite web|last=Hiatt|first=Brian|title='Star Wars' Strikes Back: Behind the Scenes of the Biggest Movie of the Year|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/features/star-wars-strikes-back-behind-the-scenes-of-the-biggest-movie-of-the-year-20151202|accessdate=2015-12-22|work=Rolling Stone|date=2015-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222050317/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/features/star-wars-strikes-back-behind-the-scenes-of-the-biggest-movie-of-the-year-20151202|archive-date=2015-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[大衛·芬奇|大衛·芬奇]]<ref>{{cite news|author=Staff|url=http://www.totalfilm.com/news/david-fincher-discusses-meeting-disney-about-star-wars-episode-vii|title=David Fincher discusses meeting Disney about Star Wars: Episode VII|work={{link-en|Total Film|Total Film}}|date=2014-09-29|accessdate=2014-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140929171818/http://www.totalfilm.com/news/david-fincher-discusses-meeting-disney-about-star-wars-episode-vii|archive-date=2014-09-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>, [[布拉德·伯德|布拉德·伯德]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Brad Bird on 'Incredibles' Sequel: 'I Would Probably Wanna Do That' (Q&A)|last=Bernardin|first=Marc|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/brad-bird-incredibles-sequel-i-523427|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2013-05-16|accessdate=2014-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607101303/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/brad-bird-incredibles-sequel-i-523427|archive-date=2013-06-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[葛雷摩·戴托羅|葛雷摩·戴托羅]]都曾被列為導演人選<ref>{{cite news|first=Kevin|last=Jagernauth|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/guillermo-del-toro-says-he-was-approached-for-star-wars-episode-7-would-have-loved-to-see-brad-bird-direct-the-sequel-20130107|title=Guillermo Del Toro Says He Was Approached For 'Star Wars: Episode 7,' Would Have Loved To See Brad Bird Direct The Sequel|work=Indiewire|date=2013-07-01|accessdate=2014-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017050618/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/guillermo-del-toro-says-he-was-approached-for-star-wars-episode-7-would-have-loved-to-see-brad-bird-direct-the-sequel-20130107|archive-date=2014-10-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2013年1月，[[J·J·亞柏拉罕|J·J·亞柏拉罕]]被選定為該片導演，而{{link-en|勞倫斯·卡斯丹|Lawrence Kasdan}}和[[賽門·金柏格|賽門·金柏格]]則成為了該片的項目顧問（{{lang-en|Project Consultant}}）<ref name="StarWarsComJan2013">{{cite web |url=http://starwars.com/news/star-wars-is-being-kick-started-with-dynamite-jj-abrams-to-direct-star-wars-episode-vii.html |title=Star Wars Is Being Kick-Started with Dynamite |publisher=StarWars.com |date=2013-01-25 |accessdate=2014-01-04 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6eR55nsV3?url=http://www.starwars.com/news/star-wars-is-being-kick-started-with-dynamite |archive-date=2016-01-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://video.cnbc.com/gallery/?play=1&video=3000146094|title=Disney Plans Stand-Alone 'Star Wars' Films|publisher=CNBC|date=2013-02-05|accessdate=2013-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130414080237/http://video.cnbc.com/gallery/?play=1&video=3000146094|archive-date=2013-04-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年10月24日，阿恩特從該項目退出，由亞柏拉罕和勞倫斯接手劇本的編寫任務（即使如此，阿恩特仍然在演職員表裡被列為該片編劇之一）<ref>{{cite news|last = Kit|first = Borys|title = Writer Michael Arndt Exits 'Star Wars: Episode VII'|url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/writer-michael-arndt-exits-star-650671|accessdate = 2013-10-24|newspaper = The Hollywood Reporter|date = 2013-10-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131026044912/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/writer-michael-arndt-exits-star-650671|archive-date = 2013-10-26|dead-url = no}}</ref>。關於阿恩特的突然退出，亞柏拉罕認為時間是主要原因<ref name="Hiatt" />，並對迪士尼將上映日期從2015年夏天延遲到同年12月表示欣慰<ref>{{cite web|last=Sullivan|first=Kevin|title=J.J. Abrams Tells Us What Will Make 'Star Wars' 'Infinitely Better'|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1718092/jj-abrams-star-wars-episode-vii-infinitely-better|accessdate=2014-05-23|publisher=MTV|date=2013-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140523214948/http://www.mtv.com/news/1718092/jj-abrams-star-wars-episode-vii-infinitely-better/|archive-date=2014-05-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亞柏拉罕和勞倫斯在[[聖莫尼卡|聖莫尼卡]]，[[紐約|紐約]]，[[巴黎|巴黎]]和[[倫敦|倫敦]]散步時確定了故事輪廓。六個星期以後，第一版劇本宣告完成<ref>{{cite web|title=Star Wars screenwriter Lawrence Kasdan on the past, present and future of 'Star Wars'|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/herocomplex/la-ca-hc-star-wars-lawrence-kasdan-20151206-story.html|first=Josh|last=Rottenberg|website=Los Angeles Times|date=2015-12-03|accessdate=2015-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211082129/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/herocomplex/la-ca-hc-star-wars-lawrence-kasdan-20151206-story.html|archive-date=2015-12-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而亞柏拉罕也在2014年1月確認了劇本已寫好的消息<ref name="WrapScript">{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/j-j-abrams-says-star-wars-episode-vii-script-done-confirms-jesse-plemons-talks|last=Molloy|first=Tim|title=J.J. Abrams Says 'Star Wars Episode VII' Script Done, Confirms Jesse Plemons Talks|work=The Wrap|date=2014-01-19|accessdate=2014-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140121010208/http://www.thewrap.com/j-j-abrams-says-star-wars-episode-vii-script-done-confirms-jesse-plemons-talks/|archive-date=2014-01-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年2月，在接受法國媒體採訪時，亞柏拉罕表示新電影的核心將回歸《星球大戰》的根源，並會將感情作為敘事核心，而不是流水線式的交代<ref name="Parismatch">{{cite web|url=http://www.parismatch.com/Culture/Livres/J-J-Abrams-un-livre-et-des-etoiles-549747|title=J.J. Abrams un livre et des étoiles|last=Micke|first=Sébastien|work={{link-en|Paris Match|Paris Match}}|date=2014-02-22|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140523225915/http://www.parismatch.com/Culture/Livres/J-J-Abrams-un-livre-et-des-etoiles-549747|archive-date=2014-05-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年4月，盧卡斯影業宣佈續集三部曲將不會借鑒《星球大戰》擴大宇宙的時間線和核心故事，但會將裡面的其他元素以其他媒介重新包裝，比如電視動畫劇集《[[星際大戰：反抗軍起義|星際大戰：反抗軍起義]]》<ref name="EUApril2014">{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/04/25/lucasfilm-clarifies-star-wars-expanded-universe|title=Lucasfilm Clarifies Star Wars Expanded Universe|last=Nicholson|first=Matt|date=2014-04-25|work=IGN|accessdate=2014-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502010126/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/04/25/lucasfilm-clarifies-star-wars-expanded-universe|archive-date=2014-05-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 前期製作 ===

2013年5月，劇組確認該片將在英國拍攝<ref name="StarWarsComUKMay2013">{{cite web|url=http://starwars.com/news/star_wars_feature_film_production_returns_to_the_uk.html|title=Star Wars Feature Film Production Returns to the U.K.|publisher=StarWars.com|date=2013-05-10|accessdate=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607134431/http://starwars.com/news/star_wars_feature_film_production_returns_to_the_uk.html|archive-date=2013-06-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，而來自盧卡斯影業的代表與英國[[財政大臣|財政大臣]][[歐思邦|歐思邦]]通過談判批准了該提議<ref name="StarWarsComUKMay2013"/>。從2013年9月開始，為了滿足亞柏拉罕的需要（他的孩子還在美國上學），位於[[壞機器人製片公司|壞機器人製片公司]]裡的製作設施被轉換成原力覺醒的拍攝地，用於拍攝並後期製作該片的部分場景<ref>{{cite news|last=Abramian|first=Alexandria|title=Source: J.J. Abrams Building 'Star Wars' Postproduction Facility in L.A. (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/star-wars-j-j-abrams-625516|accessdate=2014-03-19|newspaper=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2013-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140420083306/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/star-wars-j-j-abrams-625516|archive-date=2014-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

該片的服裝設計師是曾與亞柏拉罕在《[[星際迷航|星際迷航]]》電影中有過合作的{{link-en|邁克爾·卡普蘭|Michael Kaplan (costume designer)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/05/19/star-trek-costume-designer-joins-star-wars-vii-crew|title=Star Trek Costume Designer Joins Star Wars VII Crew|last=Butler|first=Tom|work=IGN|date=2013-05-19|accessdate=2013-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607120618/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/05/19/star-trek-costume-designer-joins-star-wars-vii-crew|archive-date=2013-06-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。JJ的御用剪輯師，{{link-en|瑪麗·喬·馬基|Mary Jo Markey}}和{{link-en|瑪莉安·布蘭登|Maryann Brandon}}，也成為了該片的剪輯師<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.studiodaily.com/2013/05/maryann-brandon-and-mary-jo-markey-on-cutting-star-trek-into-darkness|title=Maryann Brandon and Mary Jo Markey on Cutting Star Trek Into Darkness|first=Beth|last=Merchant|work=Studio Daily|date=2013-05-22|accessdate=2013-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608002252/http://www.studiodaily.com/2013/05/maryann-brandon-and-mary-jo-markey-on-cutting-star-trek-into-darkness/|archive-date=2013-06-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年8月，劇組宣佈該片的首席攝影師{{link-en|丹尼爾·明德爾|Daniel Mindel}}將用[[35毫米膠片|35毫米膠片]]攝影機（尤其是[[柯達|柯達]]5219型號）拍攝該片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/movies/column-post/jj-abrams-hires-familiar-cinematographer-shoot-star-wars-episode-vii-35mm-film-112771|title=J.J. Abrams Hires 'Star Trek' Cinematographer to Shoot 'Star Wars: Episode VII' on 35MM Film|first=Jeff|last=Sneider|publisher=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]|date=2013-08-22|accessdate=2013-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130823000213/http://www.thewrap.com/movies/column-post/jj-abrams-hires-familiar-cinematographer-shoot-star-wars-episode-vii-35mm-film-112771|archive-date=2013-08-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年10月，除了上述這三位被聘用之外，音效設計師本·伯特，特效總監克里斯·科博爾德，製作設計師里克·卡特和Dareen Gilford，混錄師Gary Rydstrom，聲音剪輯總監馬修·伍德，視效總監Roger Guyett，以及執行製片人湯米·哈珀和Jason McGatlin也成為了該片的御用主力<ref>{{cite news|last=Olsen|first=Mark|title='Star Wars: Episode VII': Lawrence Kasdan's big move|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-lawrence-kasdan-jj-abrams-star-wars-episode-vii-20131024,0,7723323.story|accessdate=2013-10-30|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2013-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030154007/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-lawrence-kasdan-jj-abrams-star-wars-episode-vii-20131024,0,7723323.story|archive-date=2013-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://starwars.com/news/master-filmmaking-team-announced-for-star-wars.html|title=Master Filmmaking Team Announced for Star Wars: Episode VII|publisher=StarWars.com|date=2013-10-24|accessdate=2014-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429014706/http://starwars.com/news/master-filmmaking-team-announced-for-star-wars.html|archive-date=2014-04-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/star-wars-episode-vii-j-j-abrams-lawrence-kasdan-to-pen-script|title='Star Wars: Episode VII': J.J. Abrams, Lawrence Kasdan to pen script|last=McIntyre|first=Gina|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2013-10-24|accessdate=2013-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027004028/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/star-wars-episode-vii-j-j-abrams-lawrence-kasdan-to-pen-script/|archive-date=2013-10-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/25/business/media/abrams-and-kasdan-take-over-writing-of-new-star-wars-movie.html|title=Abrams and Kasdan Take Over Writing of New 'Star Wars' Movie|last=Barnes|first=Brooks|work=The New York Times|date=2013-10-24|accessdate=2013-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025162515/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/25/business/media/abrams-and-kasdan-take-over-writing-of-new-star-wars-movie.html|archive-date=2013-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 演員 ===

電影的選角工程在2013年8月開始，由JJ领頭與潛在演員進行劇本閲讀和試鏡。電影的公開選角自2013年11月開始在英國，愛爾蘭和美國進行 - 數千名演員為雷切爾和托馬斯兩角試鏡<ref>{{cite web|title = Star Wars open auditions venue and dates change|url = http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-24909892|publisher = BBC News|date = 2013-11-12|accessdate = 2014-05-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140523182104/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-24909892|archive-date = 2014-05-23|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Smith|first=Jeanie|title=Disney holds St. Louis casting call for upcoming movie|url=http://www.ksdk.com/story/homepage/2013/11/09/disney-holds-casting-call-in-st-louis-for-upcoming-star-wars-film/3485605|publisher={{link-en|KSDK-TV|KSDK-TV}}|date=2013-11-09|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-url=https://archive.is/20161107161755/http://www.ksdk.com/story/homepage/2013/11/09/disney-holds-casting-call-in-st-louis-for-upcoming-star-wars-film/3485605|archive-date=2016-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Worldwide Search For Two Major Roles in Star Wars|url=http://www.opencastingcall2013.com|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151219071307/http://www.opencastingcall2013.com/|archive-date=2015-12-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2014年1月，由於卡斯丹和亞伯拉姆對劇本的改變<ref>{{cite news|title=Star Wars Episode VII A New Hope (Really)|last=Breznican|first=Anthony|work=Entertainment Weekly|date = 2014-05-16}}</ref>，選角工作重新進行。該電影的試鏡工作一直到官方公佈主角演員表（2014年4月29日）三個星期前才結束。所有試鏡過的演員與片方都簽訂了非常嚴格的保密協議，有效地禁止他們以及他們的經紀人向媒體公開任何與該片角色有關的信息<ref name="secret">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/star-wars-vii-cast-how-699964|title=How 'Star Wars' Director J.J. Abrams Kept the Cast Secret|last=Kit|first=Borys|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-04-30|accessdate=2014-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140503022957/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/star-wars-vii-cast-how-699964|archive-date=2014-05-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

雖然盧卡斯確認正傳三巨頭 - [[哈里森·福特|哈里森·福特]]、[[馬克·漢米爾|馬克·漢米爾]]和[[嘉莉·費雪|嘉莉·費雪]]將最早在2013年3月回歸該系列<ref name="BloombergMar2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2013-03-07/how-disney-bought-lucasfilm-and-its-plans-for-star-wars|title=How Disney Bought Lucasfilm—and Its Plans for 'Star Wars'|last=Leonard|first=Devin|work=Bloomberg Businessweek|date=2013-03-07|accessdate=2013-05-26|archive-date=2017-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930150541/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2013-03-07/how-disney-bought-lucasfilm-and-its-plans-for-star-wars|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但他們在該片的角色直到一年後才公佈於眾<ref name="OfficialCast"/>。[[瑟夏·羅南|瑟夏·羅南]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Saoirse Ronan Confirms She Did Audition For 'Star Wars: Episode VII' Role, But 'So Did Everyone'|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/10/01/saoirse-ronan-star-wars_n_4023967.html|date=2013-10-01|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=2013-10-01|first=Matthew|last=Jacobs|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131001225125/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/10/01/saoirse-ronan-star-wars_n_4023967.html|archive-date=2013-10-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[麥可·B·喬丹|麥可·B·喬丹]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Michael B. Jordan Confirms 'Star Wars' Rumor|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/10/10/michael-b-jordan-star-wars_n_4078714.html|first=Ryan|last=Pearson|date=2013-10-10|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109063355/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/10/10/michael-b-jordan-star-wars_n_4078714.html|archive-date=2013-11-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及[[露琵塔·尼詠歐|露琵塔·尼詠歐]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/lupita-nyongo-meets-jj-abrams-688787|title=Lupita Nyong'o Meets With J.J. Abrams for 'Star Wars: Episode VII'|last=Kit|first=Borys|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-03-14|accessdate=2014-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316205707/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/lupita-nyongo-meets-jj-abrams-688787|archive-date=2014-03-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>都曾為該片中的角色試鏡。在某個時間段，有權威報導稱劇組曾考慮讓[[傑西·普萊蒙|傑西·普萊蒙]]扮演[[盧克·天行者|盧克·天行者]]之子<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thewrap.com/star-wars-episode-vii-jesse-plemons-breaking-bad|title='Breaking Bad's' Jesse Plemons Eyed for Lead in 'Star Wars: Episode VII' (Exclusive)|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|work=The Wrap|date=2014-01-10|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140524004103/http://www.thewrap.com/star-wars-episode-vii-jesse-plemons-breaking-bad/|archive-date=2014-05-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[亞當·崔佛|亞當·崔佛]]飾演該片裡的未命名反派<ref>{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/star-wars-villain-adam-driver-girls-1201121646|title='Star Wars': Adam Driver Near Deal to Play the Villain (EXCLUSIVE)|last=Kroll|first=Justin|work=Variety|date=2014-02-26|accessdate=2014-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227071128/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/star-wars-villain-adam-driver-girls-1201121646/|archive-date=2014-02-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及讓Maisie Richardson-Sellers扮演一名未知角色<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/star-wars-episode-vii-speculation-693268|title = 'Star Wars: Episode VII' Speculation Centers on Unknown Oxford Actress|last = Kit|first = Borys|work = The Hollywood Reporter|date = 2014-04-09|accessdate = 2014-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140411024619/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/star-wars-episode-vii-speculation-693268|archive-date = 2014-04-11|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2014年3月，演員[[多米尼克·莫納漢|多米尼克·莫納漢]]透露，稱續集三部曲的劇組想讓未出名的演員扮演主要角色，而不是媒體事先報導的讓大咖來扮演主角<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/showbiz/467708/Star-Wars-Episode-VII-JJ-Abrams-looking-at-cast-of-unknown-actors-like-original-trilogy|title=JJ Abrams looking at 'unknown actors' for Star Wars Episode VII like original trilogy cast|last=Dassanayake|first=Dion|work=Express|date=2014-03-30|accessdate=2014-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330202012/http://www.express.co.uk/news/showbiz/467708/Star-Wars-Episode-VII-JJ-Abrams-looking-at-cast-of-unknown-actors-like-original-trilogy|archive-date=2014-03-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年2月，[[黛西·蕾德莉|黛西·蕾德莉]]被劇組選中成為主演，而該月月底片方與HBO達成協議，幫助崔佛調整拍攝[[女孩我最大|女孩我最大]]的時間表。同年3月，劇組與[[奧斯卡·伊薩克|奧斯卡·伊薩克]]和[[安迪·瑟克斯|安迪·瑟克斯]]就該片的角色進行會談，並一直持續到同年四月。2014年4月，[[約翰·波耶加|約翰·波耶加]]從[[傑西·歐文斯|傑西·歐文斯]]傳記片離開後，與劇組進行了會談<ref name="secret" />。丹尼斯·勞森，正傳三部曲的演員之一，被劇組邀請再次扮演該角色（Wedge Antilles），但他已“失去興趣”為由拒絶<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thecourier.co.uk/news/local/perth-kinross/new-star-wars-films-would-have-bored-me-says-scots-actor-denis-lawson-1.353349|title=New Star Wars films 'would have bored me', says Scots actor Denis Lawson|last=Topping|first=Kirsty|work=The Courier|date=2014-05-05|accessdate=2014-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512215343/http://www.thecourier.co.uk/news/local/perth-kinross/new-star-wars-films-would-have-bored-me-says-scots-actor-denis-lawson-1.353349|archive-date=2014-05-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2014年4月29日，該片的卡司通過一張在倫敦Pinewood Studios的內部劇本閲讀會上公佈<ref name="OfficialCast"/>。該照片裡包括了JJ、福特、漢米爾、瑟克斯、伊薩克、波耶加、費雪、[[多姆納爾·格里森|多姆納爾·格里森]]、安東尼·丹尼爾斯（Anthony Daniels，正傳三部曲裡扮演C3PO的演員）、蕾德莉、彼得·梅修（Peter Mayhew，丘巴卡演員）、製片人[[布賴恩·伯克|布賴恩·伯克]]、編劇卡斯丹以及盧卡斯影業總裁甘迺迪。原本該電影的卡司將在5月4日公佈（[[星際大戰日|星際大戰日]]），但由於劇組和片方擔心名單會被媒體外漏，因此提前公佈。2014年6月，劇組宣佈尼詠歐以及Gwendoline Christie將成為該電影卡司的一部分<ref name="OfficialCast2">{{cite web|url=http://www.starwars.com/news/star-wars-episode-vii-adds-academy-award-winner-lupita-nyongo-and-game-of-thrones-gwendoline-christie|title=Academy Award Winner Lupita Nyoung'o Joins the Cast of Star Wars: Episode VII|publisher=StarWars.com|date=2014-06-02|accessdate=2014-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707224037/http://www.starwars.com/news/star-wars-episode-vii-adds-academy-award-winner-lupita-nyongo-and-game-of-thrones-gwendoline-christie|archive-date=2014-07-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

為了重新準備路克一角，漢米爾連續數月沒有刮胡子，並且隨從一位私人健身師和一位營養師 - 這是為了迎合制作人希望他的身材能像老年的路克<ref name="DigitalSpy">{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a493251/star-wars-7-actors-mark-hamill-carrie-fisher-told-to-lose-weight.html|title='Star Wars 7' actors Mark Hamill, Carrie Fisher 'told to lose weight'|last=Earnes|first=Tom|date=2013-06-26|work=DigitalSpy|accessdate=2014-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502001641/http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a493251/star-wars-7-actors-mark-hamill-carrie-fisher-told-to-lose-weight.html|archive-date=2014-05-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。費雪為了準備她的角色也隨從一位私人健身師和一位營養師<ref name="DigitalSpy"/>。JJ原本希望丹尼爾斯只需要為C3PO配音<ref name=C3POdemand>{{cite web|last1=Eisenberg|first1=Eric|title=Star Wars' C-3PO Demanded These 2 Things From J.J. Abrams Before Signing His Contract|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Star-Wars-C-3PO-Demanded-2-Things-From-J-J-Abrams-Signing-His-Contract-67244.html|website=Cinemablend|accessdate=2015-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151128072215/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Star-Wars-C-3PO-Demanded-2-Things-From-J-J-Abrams-Signing-His-Contract-67244.html|archive-date=2015-11-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但劇組隨後應了丹尼爾斯的要求給他重新做了一身C3PO服<ref>{{cite web|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/09/16/star-wars-anthony-daniels-interview/2|title=Anthony Daniels' deep-dive 'Star Wars' interview: C-3PO's past, present and future|last=Hibberd|first=James|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2014-09-16|accessdate=2014-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140919011209/http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/09/16/star-wars-anthony-daniels-interview/2/|archive-date=2014-09-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年5月份，JJ在位於阿布紮比的星球大戰劇組宣布與[[UNICEF|UNICEF]]合作展開一場捐款競賽：贏家將獲得進入劇組與演職員一對一的機會<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/star-wars-episode-vii-jj-706179|title='Star Wars: Episode VII': J.J. Abrams Offers Fans a Chance to Be in Movie|last=THR Staff|date=2014-05-21|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140523175540/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/star-wars-episode-vii-jj-706179|archive-date=2014-05-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年10月，曾在星球大戰正傳和前傳三部曲都有戲份的Warwick Davis宣布他會在該片出場，但沒有公開他的角色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=124098|title=Warwick Davis Will Return for Star Wars: Episode VII, Plus Darth Vader's Star Wars Rebels Appearance Revealed|publisher=ComingSoon.net|date=2014-10-16|accessdate=2014-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113104918/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=124098|archive-date=2014-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年11月，黛比·雷諾斯（Debbie Reynolds）確認費雪的女兒，[[比莉·洛爾德|比莉·洛爾德]]，將會在該片中出現<ref name="Lourd">{{cite web|url=http://vegasseven.com/2014/11/11/debbie-reynolds-one-last-song-in-the-rain|title=Debbie Reynolds Gives a Family-Filled Curtain Call, Vegas Style|last=Rodgers|first=Lisa|work=Vegas Seven|date=2014-11-11|accessdate=2014-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141115035440/http://vegasseven.com/2014/11/11/debbie-reynolds-one-last-song-in-the-rain/|archive-date=2014-11-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。主演伊薩克的叔叔，在來劇組探望之前，被JJ邀請在片中出演一個小角色<ref>{{cite av media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UKFktbl2SjQ|title=Oscar Isaac's Uncle Scored a Role in Star Wars VII Using T-Shirts|date=2015-03-31|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|accessdate=2015-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150421020035/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UKFktbl2SjQ|archive-date=2015-04-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年12月，[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]公布了該片核心演職員的薪水：福特將會從電影中獲得2500萬[[美元|美元]]，外加0.5%的票房分成；波耶加和蕾德莉，本片的男女主角，獲得了每人46萬美元外加有條件的票房分成（假如該片全球票房突破10億美元的話）；費雪獲得了150萬美元的片酬，而本片的導演亞伯拉姆，獲得了510萬美元的底薪，外加2%的票房分成。值得一提的是，福特在《[[星際大戰四部曲：曙光乍現|星際大戰四部曲：曙光乍現]]》裏所獲得的薪水只有一萬美元<ref>{{cite news|work=The Mail|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3367360/Harrison-Ford-nets-23m-Star-Wars-s-76-times-newcomer-Daisy-Ridley.html|title=In another galaxy! Harrison Ford nets £23m from Star Wars (that's 76 times more than newcomer Daisy Ridley)|date=2015-12-19|first1=Peter|last1=Sheridan|first2=Mark|last2=Wood|accessdate=2015-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151219231913/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3367360/Harrison-Ford-nets-23m-Star-Wars-s-76-times-newcomer-Daisy-Ridley.html|archive-date=2015-12-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
在2013年11月，星際大戰七部曲公佈於2015年12月18日上映。與前六部《星際大戰》系列電影的傳統不同，本片是繼2008年8月上映之《[[星球大戰動畫：複製人戰爭_(電影)|星際大戰：複製人之戰]]》後第二部並非在5月上映的《星際大戰》電影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/11/07/star-wars-episode-vii-release-set-for-december-18-2015-breaking|title='Star Wars: Episode VII': Release set for December 18, 2015|last=Breznican|first=Anthony|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2013-11-07|accessdate=2013-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131107234953/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/11/07/star-wars-episode-vii-release-set-for-december-18-2015-breaking/|archive-date=2013-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。迪士尼在2014年3月宣布星際大戰七部曲將會推出[[IMAX|IMAX]]版本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=116262|title=Disney to Release Avengers: Age of Ultron, Star Wars: Episode VII in IMAX|work=ComingSoon.net|date=2014-03-20|accessdate=2014-03-20|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ODQJeqJ9?url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=116262|archive-date=2014-03-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年11月6日，宣布電影的正式名稱為「STAR WARS：原力覺醒」<ref name="title">{{cite web|url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/star-wars-episode-vii-title-747060|title = 'Star Wars: Episode VII' Title Revealed|last = Hayden|first = Erik|work = The Hollywood Reporter|date = 2014-11-06|accessdate = 2014-11-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109034943/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/star-wars-episode-vii-title-747060|archive-date = 2014-11-09|dead-url = no}}</ref>。在此之前大眾媒體都稱為「星際大戰七部曲」<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.theforce.net/story/front/Star_Wars_Episode_VII_Will_Be_Called_The_Force_Awakens_160763.asp|title = Star Wars: Episode VII Will Be Called The Force Awakens|author = Eric|work = TheForce.net|date = 2014-11-06|accessdate = 2014-11-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150916074352/http://www.theforce.net/story/front/Star_Wars_Episode_VII_Will_Be_Called_The_Force_Awakens_160763.asp|archive-date = 2015-09-16|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

=== 市場推廣 ===
